changelog:
Syberia OS updated!

Current build date: 10/14/2018
Minimum firmware required: 8.9.20 or 8.4.19 (depends from your battery type)
Minimum TWRP required: 3.2.3-0

Changelog:
Added Syberia Theme
Introduced Theme/Accent tile
Added partial/full screenshot QS tile
Added ability for sim cards deactivation
Support more Network modes for LTE-tile
Fixed advanced reboot powermenu toggle
Added screenshot sounds settings
Added AGPS setting menu
Updated AOSP keyboard
Changelog: prettify
Update translations

Download:  check OTA or direct https://sourceforge.net/projects/syberiaos/files/chiron/syberia_chiron-v1.2-20181014-0638-OFFICIAL.zip/download
